-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-02/kazakhstan-s-enrc-may-buy-russian-steel-plants-kommersant-says.html
Eurasian Natural Resources Corp., a
Kazakh metals company, may buy two plants in  Russia ’s Sverdlovsk
region that produce steel items and ferromanganese,  Kommersant 
reported, citing unidentified people.  To contact the reporter on this story:
